data.description: Step inside this stunning, high-end condo and feel right at home! Lovingly updated from top to bottom with great consideration! Gorgeous Patagonian rosewood floors, custom stone fireplace wall, superb kitchen remodel with high-end granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, soft close cabinets, smart cupboard design with pull out drawers and lots of storage! (SEE LIST OF FEATURES). Vaulted ceilings in the bedrooms, a rare 3 bedroom condo, and don't miss the HUGE closets! Primary suite with updated en-suite, walk-in cedar-backed custom closet and a door to your private balcony, also accessible from the kitchen. Short flight of stairs to the attached garage but all main-level living that truly feels grand! All new exterior paint as well. Take advantage of the amazing community amenities including, a lush pool oasis with a waterfall, hot tub, picnic tables & grill, gym and a gorgeous party room with full kitchen, and a library. Really the best community facilities you can find! All this luxury with a very solid and reasonable, well-run HOA. AND Sellers will contribute to buyers closing costs for rate buy down! Summerlinn is a beautiful community to live, you don't find many like this, make this gorgeous space your next home! OPEN SUNDAY 12/3, 1-3pm.
